unittitle_ssm: Harry T. Peters collection of pictorial newspaper illustrations
abstract_ssm: The collection, compiled by Harry T. Peters, includes approximately 10,500 prints (mostly black and white wood engravings) from Frank Leslie's Illustrated Newspaper, Harper's Weekly, and other publications from circa 1845 to 1920. Subject matter includes entertainment, sports, ships, politics, views of New York City, and other topics.
